original: Brise, Greta Karolina Andrea, tandläkare, Karlshamn, f. 17/12/97 i Karlshamn av tullförv. S. Aug. Svensson o. Andrea Söderlund. G. 22 m. tandl. Ivan Brise. Barn: se denne. — Stud:-ex. i Lund 16, stud. v. Lunds univ. 17, tandl :kand. 18, tandl. 20. Assist, i Växjö 20-21, praikt. i Karlshamn 21.
translated: Brise, Greta Karolina Andrea, dentist, Karlshamn, b. 17/12/97 in Karlshamn to customs official S. Aug. Svensson and Andrea Söderlund. Married in 1922 to dentist Ivan Brise. Children: see Ivan Brise's biography. - Passed matriculation exam in Lund in 1916, studied at Lund University in 1917, studied dentistry and graduated in 1920. Assistant in Växjö from 1920-1921, practiced in Karlshamn in 1921.
